title: Michael Dolan, at 27, West Roxbury resident
text:
Published By: Boston Herald - Today 
Michael “Mike” Dolan of West Roxbury died Monday in Boston. He was 27.Born and raised in West Roxbury, Mr. Dolan was a lifelong resident...
